[LunaMod Privacy Policy ]

Welcome!

This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, store, protect, and share your personal information through our services. It’s important that you read this entire policy.



What data do we store

Channel ID’s, Category ID’s, Server ID’S, User ID’s, User Warnings, Moderator ID’s, Bans, etc.



Keeping your data protected

We take a number of steps to help protect your information. All information sent within our services are encrypted both in transit and at rest. We also enforce technical and administrative access controls to limit which of our employees and contractors have access to nonpublic personal information. You can help maintain the security of your Hydra account by configuring Backup Codes.



How we use your data

We use your information for the following purposes:


To provide you with the services, To contact you, To provide customer service, To protect our services, To improve our services, To advertise our services on other platforms, etc.
